#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:2
msgid "Rust Crates"
msgstr "Rust Crate 模块"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:4
msgid ""
"Fabricatio's performance-critical components are implemented in Rust as "
"independent crates, providing high-performance routing, caching, and "
"system integration for the Python ecosystem."
msgstr "Fabricatio 的性能关键组件使用 Rust 实现为独立的 crate，为 Python 生态系统提供高性能的路由、缓存和系统集成能力。"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:8 ../../source/rust-crates.rst:424
msgid "thryd"
msgstr "thryd"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Router Engine** - High-performance LLM request routing with intelligent"
" caching and rate limiting."
msgstr "**路由引擎** - 高性能 LLM 请求路由，支持智能缓存和速率限制。"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:28
msgid "Key Features:"
msgstr "核心特性："

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Multi-Provider Routing**: OpenAI-compatible APIs, custom providers via "
"trait"
msgstr "**多提供商路由**：兼容 OpenAI 的 API，通过 trait 支持自定义提供商"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Intelligent Caching**: redb embedded database with automatic request "
"deduplication"
msgstr "**智能缓存**：基于 redb 嵌入式数据库，自动请求去重"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:32
msgid "**Token Tracking**: Accurate counting via tiktoken with TPM/RPM quotas"
msgstr "Token 追踪：基于 tiktoken 的精确计数，支持 TPM/RPM 配额"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:33
msgid "**Rate Limiting**: Sliding window algorithm (60 buckets × 60s default)"
msgstr "**速率限制**：滑动窗口算法（默认 60 个桶 × 60 秒）"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:34
msgid "**Load Balancing**: Route to multiple deployments in a group"
msgstr "**负载均衡**：将请求路由到组内的多个部署"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:35
msgid "**Async-First**: Built on Tokio for high-concurrency workloads"
msgstr "**异步优先**：基于 Tokio 构建，适用于高并发工作负载"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:36
msgid "**PyO3 Bindings**: Optional Python access via ``thryd`` Python package"
msgstr "**PyO3 绑定**：通过 ``thryd`` Python 包可选地提供 Python 访问接口"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:47
msgid "thryd Architecture"
msgstr "thryd 架构"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:83
msgid "Core Concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:85
msgid "**Providers** (``Provider`` trait)"
msgstr "**提供商** (``Provider`` trait)"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:86
msgid ""
"API service wrappers. Built-in: ``OpenAICompatible``, ``DummyProvider``. "
"Implement the trait to add custom providers."
msgstr "API 服务封装器。内置：``OpenAICompatible``、``DummyProvider``。实现该 trait 即可添加自定义提供商。"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:89
msgid "**Models** (``CompletionModel``, ``EmbeddingModel``)"
msgstr "**模型** (``CompletionModel``、``EmbeddingModel``)"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:90
msgid "Specific LLM instances with API interaction logic."
msgstr "具有 API 交互逻辑的具体 LLM 实例。"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:92
msgid "**Deployments** (``Deployment``)"
msgstr "**部署** (``Deployment``)"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:93
msgid "Models wrapped with rate limiting and usage tracking."
msgstr "封装了速率限制和使用追踪的模型。"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:95
msgid "**Routers** (``Router<CompletionTag>``, ``Router<EmbeddingTag>``)"
msgstr "**路由器** (``Router<CompletionTag>``、``Router<EmbeddingTag>``)"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:96
msgid "Manage multiple deployments, route requests by group name."
msgstr "管理多个部署，按组名路由请求。"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:120
msgid "Rate Limiting Internals"
msgstr "速率限制内部机制"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:122
msgid "Thryd uses a **sliding window algorithm** with configurable parameters:"
msgstr "Thryd 使用**滑动窗口算法**，支持以下可配置参数："

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:124
msgid "**BUCKET_COUNT**: Number of time buckets (default: 60)"
msgstr "**BUCKET_COUNT**：时间桶数量（默认：60）"

#: ../../source/rust-crates.rst:125
msgid "**BUCKETS_WINDOW_S**: Window size in seconds (default: 60)"
msgstr "**BUCKETS_WINDOW_S**：窗口大小，单位为秒（默认：60）"

